| **Start** | Begin animation | isRunning → true | "Start" → "Running" |
| **Stop** | Halt and reset | isRunning → false | Optional |
| **Pause** | Freeze in place | isPaused toggle | "Pause" ↔ "Resume" |
| **Reset** | Restore defaults | All values reset | Usually static |

